&lt;p&gt;Nuffield Health is Britain’s largest not-for-profit healthcare organisation. Join us as a General Practitioner at our onsite medical clinic in our Chester Hospital and play your part in building a healthier nation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Focusing on preventative care, as a GP with Nuffield Health you will benefit from more time with patients. What’s more, we underpin our whole system with a commitment to continuous professional development and protected learning time.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As a GP Doctor you will;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Have more time to carry out thorough assessments and get to know patients as people.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Time to be able to pay attention to the little things, in a low-stress, patient-focused environment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Connect to our network of clinical and fitness experts, which enables you to deliver a joined-up holistic service that goes far beyond diagnosis.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Use referral pathways from our state-of-the-art clinic to fitness teams/ CBT/ nutritional therapy and hospitals. This means that you can offer, and keep track of, end-to-end care for your patients.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;In return, we offer a working environment that will help you grow your skills and experience and get the best out of life. Other benefits include 25 days’ annual holiday (increasing with service), gym membership, private healthcare and a range of lifestyle and financial wellbeing benefits.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Be your best and join us in building a healthier nation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary - Dependant on experience&lt;br /&gt;Closing date - 25/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location - Chester&lt;br /&gt;Contract Type - Permanent&lt;br /&gt;Weekly Hours - 24&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;Applications will be considered as they are received and interviews will be arranged accordingly. We reserve the right to close adverts early, for example, where we have received an unprecedented high volume of applications. Therefore please apply early to ensure you are considered for the post. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
